H0.text: What dark brown food paste is the Australian version of Marmite in this country. Vegemite

H1.text: What dark brown food paste is the Australian version of Marmite in this country. Promite

H2.text: What dark brown food paste is the Australian version of Marmite in this country. MightyMite

H3.text: What dark brown food paste is the Australian version of Marmite in this country. ISnack

A4.text: Vegemite ( VEJ-uh-myte) is a brand of a thick, dark brown Australian food spread made from leftover brewers' yeast extract with various vegetable and spice additives.

A5.text: Vegemite is similar to other yeast-based spreads such as Marmite in the UK and its New Zealand version, Australian Promite, MightyMite, AussieMite, OzEmite, German Vitam-R and Swiss Cenovis.
